{"tid":1475438,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"著敵軍制服 / 間諜 都係不受日內瓦公約的保護","createTime":"2019-08-15T13:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:54:25.000Z","uid":105976,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"275b5561102c6da86e3a166b80ef2642229f21d8","tid":1475438,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"除左守軍規不攻擊非武裝人員外 <br />\n<br />\n大家要知道 間諜不受日內瓦公約的保護<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E6%97%A5%E5%86%85%E7%93%A6%E5%85%AC%E7%BA%A6/1949%E5%B9%B4/%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%AE%AE%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%AE%AE%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6#%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AD%E6%9D%A1_%E9%97%B4%E8%B0%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikisource.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2586%2585%25E7%2593%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BA%25A6%2F1949%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F%25E9%2599%2584%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%25AE%25AE%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B9%25A6%2F%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2599%2584%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%25AE%25AE%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B9%25A6%23%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%259D%25A1_%25E9%2597%25B4%25E8%25B0%258D&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg0ad0DqFW0GAicD%2BCHpJjC4%3D&h=52888705\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hant/%E6%97%A5%E5%86%85%E7%93%A6%E5%85%AC%E7%BA%A6/1949%E5%B9%B4/%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%AE%AE%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%AE%AE%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6#%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AD%E6%9D%A1_%E9%97%B4%E8%B0%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n雖然示威者未算係武裝部隊 所以黑警未致於犯左公約<br />\n但睇下佢地犯左咩原則<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第十一條 對人身的保護<br />\n一、由於第一條所指的場合而落於敵方權力下或被拘禁、拘留或以其他方式被剝奪自由的人的身心健全，不應受任何無理行為或不作為的危害。<br />\n<br />\n: 黑警對已冇力反抗人士做左咩大家有眼到啦 唔再講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第十三條 對平民醫療隊的保護的停止<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一、平民醫療隊有權享受的保護，除非用於從事人道主義職務以外的害敵行為，不應停止。</span></strong><br />\n但保護僅在發出警告，並在任何適宜時定有合理時限，而警告仍無效果後才得停止。<br />\n<br />\n: hk民平醫療隊除左人道活動冇做害敵行為 所以不應攻擊佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四十六條 間諜<br />\n一、儘管有各公約或本議定書的任何其他規定，在從事間諜行為時落於敵方權力下的衝突一方武裝部隊的任何人員，不應享受戰俘身份的權利，而得予以間諜的待遇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第三十九條 國籍標誌<br />\n二、在從事攻擊時，或為了掩護、便利、保護或阻礙軍事行動，而使用敵方的旗幟或軍用標誌、徽章或制服，是禁止的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二戰試過德軍空降師著盟軍軍服 被人捉到係就地處決</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d93746f0b1795b03a99043d4ad965d119549333c","tid":1475438,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f0020fcc26e534dfeb3b88f1c53289e286416c","tid":1475438,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16a7d932d54a944c59d00341d15a6e1f9f220f2","tid":1475438,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00f18d823d2a35c66286ad91ef37115aedd9dca","tid":1475438,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a6f104335a728a12073d217b8bd44940996c10","tid":1475438,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"中共國有無簽到日內瓦公約？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fd9866ca7347ae9ececa60c33ff839c4550040","tid":1475438,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:38:54.000Z","msg":"講多一次，宜家唔係戰爭狀態<br />\n而且就算當宜家我地同支那開戰，第一附加議定書都唔適用於非國際性武裝衝突"},{"pid":"c98bb522d26d8fecf649bc36a0427280b6fc76cc","tid":1475438,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT